MapReduce is a programing framework which allow us to perform distributed and parallel processing on large data sets in distributed environment

                                   tasks        tasks
                       ----------------------------------------------
                      |          ~> map()                            |
                      |                     ~> reduce()              |
                      |  input   ~> map()                 ~> output  |
                      |                     ~> reduce()              |
                      |          ~> map()                            |
                       ----------------------------------------------


Example:


       input                   Splitting          Mapping                 Shuffling          Reducing          Output                   K - Dear, River
                                  K                (K, V)                 K, List(V)          (K, V)            (K, V)                  V - count
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |                                           .  Dear, 1         .                                                       |
   |                       . Deer Bear River . .  Bear, 1         .                                                       |
   |                    .                      .  River, 1        .       Bear(1,1)   ...     Bear, 2                     |
   |                  .                                           .                                             Bear, 2   |
   |  Deer Bear River                         .   Car, 1          .       Car(1,1,1)  ...     Car, 3            Car, 3    |
   |  Car Car River  . . .   Car Car River  . .   Car, 1          .                                             Deer, 2   |
   |  Deer Car Bear                           .   River, 1        .       Deer(1,1)   ...     Deer, 2           River, 2  |
   |                  .                                           .                                                       |
   |                    .                     .   Deer, 1         .       River(1,1)  ...     River, 2                    |
   |                      .  Deer Car Bear  . .   Car, 1          .                                                       |
   |                                          .   Bear, 1         .                                                       |
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MapReduce Program:
    Mapper code   - write the mapper logic. How map will process the data to produce the key-value pair
    Reducer logic - reducer logic which combine the intermediate key-value pair generated by the mapper logic to give the final aggregated output
    Driver logic  - job name, input path, output path, etc



